</div>
</div>
<p><b>Decision making</b> can be regarded as an outcome of mental processes (<a href="/wiki/Cognition" title="Cognition">cognitive process</a>) leading to the selection of a course of action among several alternatives. Every decision making process produces a final <a href="/wiki/Choice" title="Choice">choice</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-reason_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-reason-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> The output can be an action or an opinion of choice.</p>
